- Look at her. She's intent on pissing me off.

532
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:18,000
Are you out of your mind?

533
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:20,400
Don't talk nonsense.

534
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:23,000
Keep calm.

535
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:30,100
