537
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:34,900
I would have died 800 times.

538
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:36,300
You're my secretary.

539
00:36:36,300 --> 00:36:37,700
Of course, I have to stay with you.

540
00:36:37,700 --> 00:36:40,400
